                            <a href="#" class="block px-4 py-2 hover:bg-gray-100">Piloter et coordonner l'activité des agences</a>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <button id="doubleDropdownButton_{{i}}" data-dropdown-toggle="doubleDropdown_{{i}}" data-dropdown-placement="right-start" type="button" class="flex items-center justify-between w-full px-4 py-2 hover:bg-gray-100">
                                Gérer la rélation client
                                <svg class="w-2.5 h-2.5 ms-3 rtl:rotate-180" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 6 10"><path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="m1 9 4-4-4-4"/></svg>
                            </button>
                            <div id="doubleDropdown_{{i}}" class="z-10 hidden bg-white border border-secondary min-w-64 divide-y divide-gray-100 rounded-lg shadow-sm w-44">
                                <div class="px-4 py-3 text-sm text-gray-900">
                                    <div class="font-medium truncate">Gérer la rélation client</div>
                                    <p id="helper-checkbox-text-{{i}}" class="text-xs font-normal text-gray-500">Veuillez sélectionner le sous processus :</p>
                                </div>
                                <ul class="py-2 text-sm text-gray-700" aria-labelledby="doubleDropdownButton_{{i}}">
